The barrels.

37:48.000 --> 37:49.320
Over there, over there,
in there.

37:53.800 --> 37:54.870
Come on.

38:06.760 --> 38:08.956
(PANTING)

38:33.480 --> 38:35.039
(MEN SHOUTING)

38:43.960 --> 38:46.156
(SOBBING)
I love you.

38:49.520 --> 38:51.830
(GUNFIRE)

39:02.800 --> 39:04.074
I love you.

39:09.560 --> 39:11.153
You should have
listened to me, Titus.

39:47.520 --> 39:48.510
Rachel.

39:59.760 --> 40:01.159
(GASPS)

40:05.120 --> 40:06.315
Rachel, hold on.

40:10.440 --> 40:12.351
(MAN SHOUTS)

40:30.320 --> 40:31.435
Rachel.

40:31.720 --> 40:34.439
