41:05.960 --> 41:08.713
Sir, you all right?
Sir.

41:08.800 --> 41:09.790
You all right, sir?

41:13.360 --> 41:15.033
Who, who are you?

41:15.120 --> 41:17.270
U.S. Government, sir.

41:17.360 --> 41:18.759
Oh.

41:18.840 --> 41:20.319
I need a medic.

41:20.400 --> 41:21.470
What?

41:26.400 --> 41:27.310
- Rachel!
- Just stay back!

41:27.400 --> 41:28.470
Let us do ourjob.

